The paper deals with histopathology image analysis using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of attention mechanisms and adaptive weighing also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the interpretability of the model, which could fall under natural language processing (cs.CL) or information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
